      - 3a **[** _(_ II _) “group entity” shall have the same meaning as assigned to the expression “group entities” in clause (_ m _) of sub-regulation (1) of regulation 2 of the International Financial Services Authority (Payment Services) Regulations, 2024 made under the International Financial Services Centres Authority Act, 2019 (50 of 2019);_ 

      - _(_ III _) “parent entity” or “principal entity” in relation to one or more other group entities, shall be an entity of which other group entities are subsidiary and such entity,—_ 

