      - ( _ii_ ) in the scheme referred to in section 124(1); and 

      - ( _iii_ ) in an approved superannuation fund; 

   - ( _i_ ) the annual accretion by way of interest, dividend or any other amount of similar nature during the tax year to the balance at the credit of the fund or scheme referred to in clause ( _h_ ), computed in such manner, as may be prescribed (to the extent it relates to the contribution referred to in the said clause in any tax year). 

