   - ( _ii_ ) the members holding 75% or more voting rights in the amalgamating co-operative bank become members of the amalgamated co-operative bank; and 

   - ( _iii_ ) the shareholders holding 75% or more in value of the shares in the amalgamating co-operative bank (other than the shares held by the amalgamated co-operative bank or its nominee or its subsidiary, immediately before the merger) become shareholders of the amalgamated co-operative bank; 

