- ( _b_ ) where the total income determined under section 270(1)( _a_ ) or assessed, reassessed or recomputed in a preceding order is a loss, the amount of tax calculated on the under-reported income as if it were the total income; 

- ( _c_ ) in any other case, determined as follows— 

